---
layout: base.njk
title: "Amenities | Mona Shores Flats"
description: "See what's included: granite kitchens, in-unit laundry, fitness center, pickleball courts, dog run, playground, clubhouse and detached garages in Norton Shores, MI."
---

<section class="section" style="padding-top:clamp(110px,14vw,180px)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="stack" data-reveal>
      <div class="eyebrow">What's Included</div>
      <h2>What's included?</h2>
      <p class="lead">A brand-new 2025 community — real photos of the actual finishes and spaces, plus the everyday extras that come standard.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- In your home -->
    <div class="amen-group">
      <div class="amen-group__head" data-reveal><h3>In your home</h3><span>Every floor plan, standard</span></div>
      <div class="acards" data-reveal>
        <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/kitchen.jpg" alt="Granite island kitchen with stainless appliances" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>Granite Kitchens</strong><span>Island layouts · stainless</span></figcaption></figure>
        <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/living.jpg" alt="Open-concept living room" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>Open Living</strong><span>High ceilings · balcony access</span></figcaption></figure>
        <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/laundry.jpg" alt="In-unit washer and dryer" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>In-Unit Laundry</strong><span>Full-size W/D</span></figcaption></figure>
        <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/bathroom.jpg" alt="Bathroom with granite vanity" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>Granite Baths</strong><span>Modern fixtures</span></figcaption></figure>
        <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/bedroom.jpg" alt="Spacious carpeted bedroom" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>Quiet Bedrooms</strong><span>Plush &amp; bright</span></figcaption></figure>
        <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/closet.jpg" alt="Generous bedroom closet" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>Generous Closets</strong><span>Real storage</span></figcaption></figure>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Around the community -->
    <div class="amen-group">
      <div class="amen-group__head" data-reveal><h3>Around the community</h3><span>Shared spaces for residents</span></div>
      <div class="acards" data-reveal>
        <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/gym.jpg" alt="On-site fitness center" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>Fitness Center</strong><span>Cardio · strength · Peloton</span></figcaption></figure>
        <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/courtyard.jpg" alt="Private balcony with French doors" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>Private Balconies</strong><span>Off every living area</span></figcaption></figure>
        <figure class="acard"><img src="/img/building.jpg" alt="Mona Shores Flats grounds" loading="lazy"><figcaption class="acard__label"><strong>Landscaped Grounds</strong><span>2025 construction</span></figcaption></figure>
      </div>
      <div class="incl" data-reveal>
        {% for c in site.community %}
        <div class="incl__item"><strong>{{ c.name }}</strong><span>{{ c.note }}</span></div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <p class="muted" style="font-size:.86rem;margin-top:16px">We're still photographing the pickleball courts, dog run, playground and clubhouse — they're brand new. <a href="/contact/#tour" style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:600">Come see them in person →</a></p>
    </div>

    <!-- Everything included -->
    <div class="amen-group">
      <div class="amen-group__head" data-reveal><h3>Everything included</h3></div>
      <ul class="checklist" data-reveal>
        {% for a in site.amenities %}<li>{{ a.name }}</li>{% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section cta">
  <div class="wrap stack center">
    <h2>Come see it in person.</h2>
    <p>{{ site.special }}</p>
    <div class="cta__actions">
      <a class="btn btn--light btn--lg" href="/contact/#tour">Schedule a Tour</a>
      <a class="btn btn--accent btn--lg" href="{{ site.urls.availability }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Check Availability →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
